      "writtenOn": "2017-11-15T23:20:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "if console.html were able to check it, what would it return? Can we return #invalid-build-id and return it as is in console.html? That would be a better link than a bogus one because it will not take the user to a non-existing page but more clearly communicate that a build ID is invalid.",
      "parentUuid": "120e8e33_49913cd6",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 36,
